---
title: AI Copilot Chat Flow - Request Processing Sequence
---

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as AI Copilot Panel
    participant API as AiCopilotController
    participant Conv as ConversationService
    participant Sup as SupervisorAgent
    participant Reg as AgentRegistry
    participant Agent as DomainAgent
    participant LLM as OpenAiLlmService
    participant GPT as OpenAI GPT-5 Mini
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Audit as AI Audit Trail

    User->>UI: Types message
    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/ai/chat
    API->>Conv: processMessage(request, user)

    Note over Conv: Get/Create Conversation
    Conv->>DB: Save user message

    Note over Sup: Route to appropriate agent
    Conv->>Sup: route(message, moduleContext)
    Sup->>LLM: chat(supervisorPrompt, message)
    LLM->>GPT: Chat Completion API
    GPT-->>LLM: {targetAgent, reasoning, refinedQuery}
    LLM-->>Sup: RoutingDecision
    Sup-->>Conv: targetAgent = CAPA_AGENT

    Note over Conv: Execute target agent
    Conv->>Reg: getAgent(CAPA_AGENT)
    Reg-->>Conv: CapaAgent instance

    Conv->>Agent: execute(agentRequest)
    Agent->>LLM: chat(capaPrompt, refinedQuery)
    LLM->>GPT: Chat Completion API
    GPT-->>LLM: Response content
    LLM-->>Agent: LlmResponse
    Agent-->>Conv: AgentResponse

    Note over Conv: Persist results
    Conv->>DB: Save assistant message
    Conv->>DB: Save agent execution
    Conv->>Audit: Log AI action

    Conv-->>API: AiChatResponse
    API-->>UI: {conversationId, content, agentType}
    UI-->>User: Display response with agent badge
